ExtFUSE: add callbacks to scope

The BPF program using ExtFUSE needs access also to the following BPF
functions: bpf_tail_call and bpf_trace_printk.
Add these functions to the ExtFUSE program scope.

Signed-off-by: Alessio Balsini <balsini@android.com>
